  "detailed_description": "In the Valley of Death is a color-based hack, slash, and dash twin-stick shooter in a top-down perspective that follows the adventures of Red and Blue as they battle their way through hordes of enemies and attempt to make their way to the Valley of Death.<br><br>In the Valley of Death features a unique set of mechanics where the player controls Red and Blue, each character having their set of abilities, as they fight their way through colored enemies, where each enemy is vulnerable to a weapon with the same color they have, providing players with a unique challenge as they venture further into the game.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unique Gun, Slash, and Dash Gameplay Mechanic</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1762560/extras/c447917723c916be29240a1cfc3dc96c.poster.avif?t=1633956525\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1762560/extras/c447917723c916be29240a1cfc3dc96c.webm?t=1633956525\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1762560/extras/c447917723c916be29240a1cfc3dc96c.mp4?t=1633956525\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Hectic High Intensity Fights.</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1762560/extras/03711a55ff01c68c8037e09d196de79a.poster.avif?t=1633956525\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1762560/extras/03711a55ff01c68c8037e09d196de79a.webm?t=1633956525\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1762560/extras/03711a55ff01c68c8037e09d196de79a.mp4?t=1633956525\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></sp